Package: onefile
Source: onefile
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Section: utils
Maintainer: Andrea de Candia andy.decandia@gmail.com
Homepage: <https://github.com/andrea-de/onefile>
Description: A command-line tool to combine files for use in AI-assisted development, specifically tailored for efficient input preparation in interactive LLM sessions. It addresses the limitations of AI-integrated code editors by offering flexibility in supporting various LLMs.
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), dh-make
Depends: ${misc:Depends}